{"article_id":"3rApEI2qEuqvZRLQ","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh testifies during the second day of his confirmation hearing before the Senate Judiciary Committee on Capitol Hill in Washington , D.C. , September 5 , 2018 .","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"( Joshua Roberts/Reuters )","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"If Ford won ' t agree to testify ,","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"hold the vote tomorrow","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"as planned .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"In my column yesterday , I contended","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"that the unverifiable sexual-assault allegation against Judge Brett Kavanaugh bore \" all the hallmarks of a set-up. \"","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"I based that assessment on the patently flimsy evidence ,","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"coupled with Senate Democrats ' duplicitous abuse of the confirmation-hearing process .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"To repeat myself :","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"If the Democrats had raised the allegation in a timely manner ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"its weakness would have been palpable ,","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"it would have been used","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"for what little it ' s worth","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"in examining Kavanagh during his days of testimony ,","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"it would be put to rest as unverifiable ,","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"and we ' d be on to a confirmation vote .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"Instead , we ' re on to a delay","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"- precisely the Democrats ' objective .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"They want to slow-walk Kavanaugh ' s confirmation vote until after the midterms , in the hopes","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"that they swing the Senate in their favor","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"and have the numbers","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"to defeat the nomination .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Well , whaddaya know :","depth":4},{"id":24,"text":"Late last night , the partisan Democratic attorneys","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"retained by the putative victim , Christine Blasey Ford ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"delivered a letter to Senator Chuck Grassley","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"( R. , Iowa ) ,","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"the Judiciary Committee chairman ,","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"contending","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"that before any hearing","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"at which she is summoned to testify","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"takes place ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"there must be a \" full investigation by law enforcement officials","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"[ to ] ensure","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"that the crucial facts and witnesses in this matter are assessed in a non-partisan manner . \"","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"My personal favorite part of the missive is the lawyers ' complaint","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"that ,","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"based on published reports ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"it seems that some of the senators have already \" made up their minds \" about Professor Ford ' s story .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"This takes some gumption ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"coming from Democratic activists","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"who are working in tandem with Democratic senators","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"who decided to vote against Judge Kavanaugh","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"long before the hearing started .","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"The lawyers utter this tripe","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"while in the middle of a transparent gambit","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"to block the nomination","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"by delaying it interminably","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"- or at least until after the November election .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"The committee had invited Ford to testify at a hearing on Monday of next week","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"( September 24 ) .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"This was more solicitude than the allegation merits","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"given the Democrats ' willful abuse of the process .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"Ford should have been invited to submit her claims in writing ,","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"Kavanaugh could have been asked to respond ,","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"and the committee could have assessed the allegation","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"- a 36-year-old alleged incident","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"that the claimed victim , then 15 , did not mention for 30 years ,","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"can not fix in time and place ,","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"and claimed to want anonymity about ,","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"and which is flatly denied by the only other witnesses , Kavanaugh and his friend Mark Judge , then 17-year-old high-school students .","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"The committee could have weighed Ford ' s allegation against the mountain of contrary information","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"posited in favor of Kavanaugh ' s character , and his treatment of women and girls , professionally and socially , over the last three dozen years .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"( There is also ,","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"we might remember ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"the - apparently -","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"small matter of the 300 appellate opinions","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"Kavanaugh has penned since his appointment twelve years ago to one of the nation ' s most distinguished courts . )","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"As in any formal proceeding","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"( other than a kangaroo court ) ,","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"the committee could also have considered","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"that the partisans with the greatest incentive","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"to publicize derogatory information about Kavanaugh","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"- if they believed it to be true -","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"instead sat on it ,","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"springing it at the last second in a palpable attempt","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"to obstruct the committee ' s vote on the nomination","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"( which they were certain to lose ) .","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"The committee vote ,","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"scheduled for Thursday ,","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"could have gone forward .","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"Instead , the vote was delayed","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"to provide Ford an opportunity","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"to testify .","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"This was wholly unnecessary under the circumstances ,","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"but the committee went the extra mile","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"in order to exhibit sensitivity to Ford ' s alleged trauma .","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"Rather than accept , however ,","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"Ford ' s partisan Democratic lawyers countered","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"that there must be an investigation first","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"- never mind that the committee hearing is an investigation of the only thing","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"that matters :","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"how the Senate should exercise its constitutional advice-and-consent duty .","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"First , in no case does even the most sympathetic , convincing victim of a crime get to dictate the terms of the investigation .","depth":4},{"id":95,"text":"Second , in any sexual-assault investigation , an interview of the alleged victim is among the first things","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"that must be done .","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"Here , moreover , it would be the first thing ,","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"since after 36 years a forensic investigation is not possible .","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"Because the alleged victim ' s version of events would dictate the course of the rest of the investigation ,","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"it would be absurd to delay an interview .","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"Third ,","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"as long as Ford ' s counsel want to talk about regular , independent investigations ,","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"we should note","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"that there is not a police organization in America","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"that would entertain her allegation , in light of the lapse of time and the long-ago exhaustion of the statute of limitations .","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"Professional investigators understand only too well the inherent unreliability of allegations","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"raised in the manner","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"Ford ' s have been raised .","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"The only relevance of this alleged incident is to a Senate function ,","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"so it is for the Senate committee to decide how to proceed .","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"Fourth ,","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"as Ford ' s lawyers well know ,","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"in our adversary system , we do not submit disputes to a team of independent expert investigators .","depth":13},{"id":114,"text":"We have advocates for each side","depth":15},{"id":115,"text":"- partisans -","depth":15},{"id":116,"text":"make the case","depth":16},{"id":117,"text":"as well","depth":16},{"id":118,"text":"as it can be made from their side ' s perspective ,","depth":15},{"id":119,"text":"and we let the other side attack with all its partisan might .","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"We allow each side to examine the other ' s witnesses .","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"Based on this often heated clash , we expect","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"that members of the public will be able to figure out what information is reliable ,","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"what is nonsense ,","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"and what the truth is .","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"That is the process","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"we use","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"for deciding life-and-death criminal sentences , as well as civil judgments","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"that can be financially ruinous .","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"We have used it for centuries","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"because it works .","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"It is fashionable throat-clearing at this point to offer some vertiginous , ostentatiously sympathetic twaddle about how Professor Ford is credible in the sense","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"that she truly believes what she has claimed , yet mistaken about . . . well . . . everything","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"that matters .","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"Sorry ,","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"I ' m a simple man .","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"What ' s happening here is pure BS .","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"I don ' t know","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"if something awful really happened to Ford","depth":14},{"id":139,"text":"when she was 15 .","depth":14},{"id":140,"text":"None of us will ever know .","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"Apparently , Ford herself does not know basic facts either ,","depth":13},{"id":142,"text":"since she can not tell us where and when the alleged assault happened ,","depth":14},{"id":143,"text":"and what she did in the aftermath .","depth":14},{"id":144,"text":"Giving her the benefit of the doubt","depth":14},{"id":145,"text":"that it happened","depth":15},{"id":146,"text":"as she claims","depth":16},{"id":147,"text":"it happened ,","depth":16},{"id":148,"text":"she hasn ' t come close to establishing","depth":15},{"id":149,"text":"that Brett Kavanaugh ,","depth":17},{"id":150,"text":"as opposed to some other kid","depth":18},{"id":151,"text":"she has forgotten ,","depth":18},{"id":152,"text":"was her assailant ;","depth":16},{"id":153,"text":"that is , she has not established","depth":15},{"id":154,"text":"that her memory of the assailant can be trusted","depth":16},{"id":155,"text":"when she can not recall other rudimentary details .","depth":16},{"id":156,"text":"We can feel sympathy for her","depth":12},{"id":157,"text":"while nevertheless inferring","depth":13},{"id":158,"text":"that she does not want to testify","depth":14},{"id":159,"text":"because she can not explain the oddities of her account .","depth":14},{"id":160,"text":"Or we can justifiably suspect","depth":12},{"id":161,"text":"that the whole thing is a partisan stunt .","depth":12},{"id":162,"text":"If Democrats had believed","depth":13},{"id":163,"text":"Ford ' s story was convincing ,","depth":14},{"id":164,"text":"and had followed the committee-hearing process in good faith ,","depth":14},{"id":165,"text":"we ' d have heard about it in July ,","depth":12},{"id":166,"text":"and we ' d have been hearing about nothing else since","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"- especially during the hours upon hours","depth":13},{"id":168,"text":"that Kavanaugh answered aggressively provocative , politically loaded questions under oath .","depth":13},{"id":169,"text":"Senator Feinstein knew about Ford ' s allegation all that time","depth":12},{"id":170,"text":"and never uttered a peep about it - not in face-to-face interviews with Kavanaugh or in her rounds of questioning at the hearing .","depth":12},{"id":171,"text":"And don ' t tell me","depth":14},{"id":172,"text":"Feinstein had to stay mum","depth":14},{"id":173,"text":"to honor Ford ' s desire for anonymity .","depth":13},{"id":174,"text":"There is good reason","depth":14},{"id":175,"text":"to believe","depth":15},{"id":176,"text":"Ford had no intention","depth":17},{"id":177,"text":"of remaining anonymous","depth":17},{"id":178,"text":"( hiring Democrat-activist lawyers ,","depth":17},{"id":179,"text":"taking a polygraph , etc. ) .","depth":17},{"id":180,"text":"But","depth":15},{"id":181,"text":"even if Ford truly wanted to remain unidentified ,","depth":16},{"id":182,"text":"Senator Feinstein could easily have questioned Kavanaugh about the purported incident","depth":17},{"id":183,"text":"without mentioning Ford ' s name .","depth":17},{"id":184,"text":"That would have preserved anonymity","depth":15},{"id":185,"text":"while adhering to the hearing process .","depth":15},{"id":186,"text":"Instead , the Democrats ' ranking committee member contemptuously undermined the committee ' s process ,","depth":10},{"id":187,"text":"and now other Senate Democrats are following her lead .","depth":10},{"id":188,"text":"In the meantime , Judge Kavanaugh is presumed innocent ,","depth":10},{"id":189,"text":"and his unambiguous claim of innocence rings true in the context of everything else","depth":11},{"id":190,"text":"we have learned about him .","depth":11},{"id":191,"text":"When someone is accused of criminal conduct ,","depth":12},{"id":192,"text":"the burden is not supposed to be on the accused to convince us","depth":13},{"id":193,"text":"that it didn ' t happen .","depth":13},{"id":194,"text":"There must first be convincing evidence","depth":13},{"id":195,"text":"that it did happen","depth":13},{"id":196,"text":"before the accused is called on to answer the charge .","depth":12},{"id":197,"text":"Yet Judge Kavanaugh did not remain silent .","depth":12},{"id":198,"text":"He has insisted on answering ,","depth":13},{"id":199,"text":"essentially proclaiming :","depth":14},{"id":200,"text":"\" It is not just that I am not guilty ;","depth":16},{"id":201,"text":"I am innocent .","depth":16},{"id":202,"text":"It is not just that this allegation hasn ' t come close to being proved ;","depth":17},{"id":203,"text":"I did not do it .","depth":17},{"id":204,"text":"And I am prepared to testify to that effect , publicly or in closed session , anytime , anyplace . \"","depth":16},{"id":205,"text":"As I argued yesterday ,","depth":13},{"id":206,"text":"you are not going to have decent , meritorious people in law and politics","depth":13},{"id":207,"text":"if Democrats are permitted to mug Kavanaugh the way","depth":14},{"id":208,"text":"they mugged Judge Bork and Justice Thomas ,","depth":14},{"id":209,"text":"the way","depth":14},{"id":210,"text":"they try to mug every Republican judicial candidate","depth":15},{"id":211,"text":"whose nomination threatens to close off the courts as an avenue of radical social change","depth":16},{"id":212,"text":"- i.e. , whose confirmation makes it more likely that the Left will have to try to convince voters and lawmakers in the democratic process ,","depth":17},{"id":213,"text":"rather than have unaccountable judges impose progressive pieties .","depth":17},{"id":214,"text":"The long-term goal here is to make the judicial-confirmation process so notoriously savage and demeaning","depth":11},{"id":215,"text":"that no sensible , well-meaning conservative or moderate person would agree to put himself and his family through it .","depth":11},{"id":216,"text":"The idea is to stock the courts with nothing but progressives and mediocrities","depth":11},{"id":217,"text":"willing to roll over for progressives .","depth":11},{"id":218,"text":"It is a disgrace that this should happen in this republic , and in connection with the courts ,","depth":10},{"id":219,"text":"which are not supposed to be political forces ,","depth":11},{"id":220,"text":"but which have been converted into an uber-political institution","depth":12},{"id":221,"text":"that progressives are desperate to control .","depth":12},{"id":222,"text":"The short-term goal is to delay Kavanaugh ' s nomination .","depth":9},{"id":223,"text":"Democrats should not be allowed to get away with it .","depth":9},{"id":224,"text":"Give Professor Ford until noon today to accept the committee ' s unnecessarily indulgent invitation","depth":11},{"id":225,"text":"to testify on Monday .","depth":11},{"id":226,"text":"If she has not accepted by the deadline ,","depth":11},{"id":227,"text":"Senator Grassley should proceed with the committee vote tomorrow","depth":13},{"id":228,"text":"( Thursday )","depth":13},{"id":229,"text":"as previously scheduled .","depth":12},{"id":230,"text":"If Democrats scream bloody murder ,","depth":11},{"id":231,"text":"who cares ?","depth":11},{"id":232,"text":"They ' re a one-trick pony .","depth":11},{"id":233,"text":"They are going to scream bloody murder","depth":13},{"id":234,"text":"no matter when the votes are taken .","depth":13},{"id":235,"text":"No more delay .","depth":13},{"id":236,"text":"It only rewards the mugging","depth":14},{"id":237,"text":"and encourages more of it .","depth":14}],"relations":[{"parent":475,"left":242,"right":474,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":242,"left":239,"right":241,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":239,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":241,"left":2,"right":240,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":240,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":474,"left":272,"right":473,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":272,"left":259,"right":271,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":259,"left":253,"right":258,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":253,"left":245,"right":252,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":245,"left":243,"right":244,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":243,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":244,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":252,"left":9,"right":251,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":251,"left":10,"right":250,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":250,"left":11,"right":249,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":249,"left":248,"right":16,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":248,"left":247,"right":15,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":247,"left":12,"right":246,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":246,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":258,"left":254,"right":257,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":254,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":257,"left":19,"right":256,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":256,"left":20,"right":255,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":255,"left":21,"right":22,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":271,"left":23,"right":270,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":270,"left":263,"right":269,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":263,"left":260,"right":262,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":260,"left":24,"right":25,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":262,"left":261,"right":28,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":261,"left":26,"right":27,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":269,"left":29,"right":268,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":268,"left":265,"right":267,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":265,"left":264,"right":32,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":264,"left":30,"right":31,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":267,"left":33,"right":266,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":266,"left":34,"right":35,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":473,"left":329,"right":472,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":329,"left":285,"right":328,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":285,"left":281,"right":284,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":281,"left":280,"right":45,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":280,"left":36,"right":279,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":279,"left":274,"right":278,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":274,"left":37,"right":273,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":273,"left":38,"right":39,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":278,"left":40,"right":277,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":277,"left":41,"right":276,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":276,"left":42,"right":275,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":275,"left":43,"right":44,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":284,"left":46,"right":283,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":283,"left":47,"right":282,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":282,"left":48,"right":49,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":328,"left":303,"right":327,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":303,"left":288,"right":302,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":288,"left":286,"right":287,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":286,"left":50,"right":51,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":287,"left":52,"right":53,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":302,"left":295,"right":301,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":295,"left":289,"right":294,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":289,"left":54,"right":55,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":294,"left":56,"right":293,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":293,"left":57,"right":292,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":292,"left":58,"right":291,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":291,"left":59,"right":290,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":290,"left":60,"right":61,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":301,"left":296,"right":300,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":296,"left":62,"right":63,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":300,"left":297,"right":299,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":297,"left":64,"right":65,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":299,"left":66,"right":298,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":298,"left":67,"right":68,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":327,"left":321,"right":326,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":321,"left":312,"right":320,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":312,"left":305,"right":311,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"p